snippet.title: Tomb of Trials - Promo Video
snippet.description:
Tomb of Trials is my new game for PC/Mac. It was codeveloped with Jeff Goldenberg.

Get it here:
https://vectordyne.itch.io/tomb-of-trials



Tomb of Trials is a adventure, puzzle, platformer game where the player must escape from an ancient tomb full of mysteries.  Do you have what it takes for escape the Tomb of Trials?
